Author:     mikoto miura <johnd@MacBook-Air.local>
AuthorDate: Wed May 13 15:57:43 2026 +0900
Commit:     mikoto miura <johnd@MacBook-Air.local>
CommitDate: Fri May 15 15:47:11 2026 +0900

    docs(security): security-hardening-pre-m10 P0 scaffold (SH-0〜SH-5 ADR)
    
    Codex 12th review (codex_issue.md) 5 件統合消化タスクの設計確定。
    
    ## Scope (docs+steering only)
    
    - `.steering/20260513-security-hardening-pre-m10/` 配下 7 files (952 insertions)
    - 本 commit は source 変更ゼロ、M9 baseline 不可侵
    - PR #161 (.gitattributes) で §6 LOW は事前 close 済、残 5 件を本タスクで close
    
    ## 主要判断 (decisions.md ADR)
    
    - **SH-0 (meta)**: /reimagine 代替プロセス。Plan agent enumeration + AskUserQuestion
      で「破壊と構築」の構造的要件を満たし、同一 design への skill 再起動は user
      choice と矛盾する案を生むため bypass。empirical 検証は Codex 13th review で担う
    - **SH-1**: hook (first-line nuisance) + CI (final defense) 2 層。既存
      eval-egress-grep-gate 同型
    - **SH-2**: WS 3-layer auth (token + Origin + cap=8)、`require_token=False` default
      (back-compat、Godot patch を別 PR)、AskUserQuestion 採用
    - **SH-3**: `network_access=false` + `web_search="live"` 維持 (memory
      project_m9_b_plan_pr.md の SGLang v0.3+ 発見実績を保護)
    - **SH-4**: symlink reject + prefix allowlist + `--overwrite-memory-db` flag、
      既存 `--overwrite` 3-flag パターン port
    - **SH-5**: heartbeat (maxsize=1 coalesce) + main (1024 drop-oldest + ErrorMsg
      warning) の 2-queue 分離、`SCHEMA_VERSION` 不変で M9 baseline 保護
    
    ## Phase plan
    
    P1 §3 → P2 §4 → P3 §5 → P4 §2 → P5 §1 → P6 Codex 13th review → P7 Closure (~18h、2-3 days)
    
    Refs: /Users/johnd/.claude/plans/agile-chasing-sifakis.md (approved Plan)
    
    Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>

