    feat(cli): eval --memory-db symlink+prefix+overwrite guard (SH-4)
    
    SH-4 ADR per `.steering/20260513-security-hardening-pre-m10/decisions.md`、
    codex_issue.md §4 MEDIUM/LOW を close。
    
    ## 変更
    
    - `cli/eval_run_golden.py` — `ALLOWED_MEMORY_DB_PREFIX_STRINGS` constant
      (`/tmp/p3a_natural_`, `/tmp/erre-`) + `_ALLOWED_MEMORY_DB_TMP_BASENAME_PREFIXES`
      (macOS `/tmp` → `/private/tmp` symlink 正規化対応の basename prefix)
    - `cli/eval_run_golden.py` — `_is_allowed_memory_db_prefix(path)` + `_resolve_memory_db_path(path, *, persona, run_idx, overwrite)` helper
      - ``path is None`` → 既存 ME-2 default `/tmp/p3a_natural_<persona>_run<idx>.sqlite`
        を scratch として auto-unlink (back-compat)
      - explicit path → symlink reject + prefix allowlist + 既存ファイル時
        `--overwrite-memory-db` 必須
    - `cli/eval_run_golden.py` `capture_natural()` — signature に
      `overwrite_memory_db: bool = False` 追加、L1023-1030 の unconditional unlink
      を helper 経由に置換
    - `cli/eval_run_golden.py` argparse — `--overwrite-memory-db` flag 追加
      (`--force-rescue` の直後、既存 3-flag escalation パターンに整合)
    - `main()` — `capture_natural(..., overwrite_memory_db=args.overwrite_memory_db)`
    - `tests/test_cli/test_eval_run_golden.py` — 5 red-team ケース追加:
      - symlink reject
      - prefix outside allowlist reject
      - explicit existing file refuses without overwrite
      - explicit existing file accepts with overwrite (unlink + same Path return)
      - default (`None`) branch preserves auto-unlink back-compat
    
    ## 検証
    
    - `uv run ruff check src tests` → All checks passed
    - `uv run ruff format --check src tests` → 207 files already formatted
    - `uv run mypy src` → Success: no issues found in 80 source files
    - `uv run pytest -q -m "not godot and not eval and not spike and not training and not inference"`
      → 1341 passed, 31 skipped, 52 deselected (回帰 0)
    - `uv run pytest tests/test_cli/test_eval_run_golden.py -q -m eval` → 27 passed (+5 new)
    
    ## M9 baseline 不可侵
    
    - `data/eval/golden/` 30 cells / `src/erre_sandbox/evidence/` への変更 0
    - `schemas.py` SCHEMA_VERSION (`0.10.0-m7h`) 不変
    - 既存 P3a-finalize Phase B+C baseline の rerun-compatibility 維持
      (default ME-2 path semantics 完全保持)
    
