CommitDate: Fri May 15 16:11:56 2026 +0900

    feat(world): bounded envelope queue + warning (SH-5)
    
    world/tick.py の単一 unbounded asyncio.Queue を 2-queue split に改修。
    - heartbeat queue (maxsize=1, coalesce / latest-wins)
    - main queue (maxsize=1024, drop-oldest + ErrorMsg runtime_backlog_overflow)
    
    3 put 経路 (inject_envelope / _consume_result / _on_heartbeat_tick) と
    2 consumer (recv_envelope / drain_envelopes) を新 helper と coalesce
    ロジックに統合。SCHEMA_VERSION 不変、data/eval/golden 変更ゼロで M9
    baseline 保護。
    
    具体的な変更:
    - 新 module-level helper _make_runtime_error (gateway._make_error の
      duplicate、world → integration の逆向き依存を回避)
    - 新 private method _enqueue_with_drop_oldest (Registry.fan_out 同型)
    - recv_envelope: asyncio.wait(FIRST_COMPLETED) + main 優先 race-merge、
      pending getter は contextlib.suppress(CancelledError) で吸収
    - drain_envelopes: heartbeat → main の順で取り出し、既存の
      test_drain_is_fifo / test_heartbeat の順序契約を保持
    - integration/protocol.py MAX_ENVELOPE_BACKLOG の docstring を
      「runtime も bounded」に更新
    
    既存テストの mechanical 調整 (coalesce 仕様の帰結):
    - test_heartbeat_emits_world_tick_msgs_periodically: 5 個 → 1 個 expect
      (heartbeat coalesce は SH-5 ADR の核心仕様)
    
    新規テスト 2 ケース:
    - test_envelope_queue_overflow_emits_warning_and_drops_oldest
    - test_heartbeat_queue_coalesces_to_latest
    
    検証 5 stage 全緑 (新 11 / 周辺 182 / ruff+mypy / 全 1378 / baseline diff 0)。
    
    Refs: .steering/20260513-security-hardening-pre-m10/decisions.md SH-5
    Refs: gateway.Registry.fan_out (L208-261) reference pattern
    
    Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>

